_:N1978bcaa126341db888eeecb4e4b9dde <http://schema.org/description> "The Valuation Tribunal Service (VTS) is an administrative statutory body. It supports the Valuation Tribunal for England in its work dealing with appeals about Council Tax and non-domestic (business) rates. VTS is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
